<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n38006c"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n38" href="#n38006c">N38 (VI.B.32)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n38all.htm#n38006c"> 6(c)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> releache / riposi </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Fr. <i>Rela&acirc;che</i>: a period of rest. The word is also applied to the off-season periods during which opera houses and theatres are closed. The Italian <i>riposo</i> (plural <i>riposi</i>) means the same thing. </mm> </dd></dl>
